:.START

Treasury plan to raise $1.8 billion in new cash wit di sale Monday of about $15.6 billion in short term to redeem $13.8 billion in restructuring bill.

Di total na from 13 weeks to 26 weeks bill wey go dey March 1, 1990 and May 3, 1990.

Di funds wey dey di bill, wey dey available at least ten thousand, na im de must get by 1 p.m. for di Treasury, or Federal Reserve Bank, or branch office.

Treasury yarn sey e go alter di auction unless sey e don assure state by law to raise di statutory amount before di scheduled auction on Monday.

